<TEXT>
More than two dozen serious fraud prosecutions are awaiting trial or making
their way through the courts.
Those involved include:
Mr Kevin Maxwell, accused of conspiracy to defraud and theft, and Mr Ian
Maxwell, accused of conspiracy to defraud. Their case is still before
