Mr Asil Nadir, former chairman of Polly Peck International, whose trial on
16 theft charges is scheduled to start at
the Old Bailey next March and is expected to last six months.
Mr Roger Levitt, head of the Levitt group, whose trial on fraud charges is
expected next year.
Mr Gordon Layton, chief executive of National Car Parks, accused of
