the factory, but disclosed no figures. It said that after the new machinery
was installed, RJR-Petro's annual production capacity would rise to 22bn
cigarettes, to make it Russia's largest cigarette producer.
American-blend brands 'will be phased in as component sourcing is resolved',
RJR said.
