<HEADLINE>
FT  16 JUL 92 / UK Company News: Leslie Wise 12% ahead at Pounds 1.51m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
In spite of unfavourable trading conditions Leslie Wise, the textiles,
women's clothing and knitted fabrics group, lifted profits from Pounds 1.35m
to Pounds 1.51m pre-tax for the year to May 31.
The near-12 per cent advance was scored from a 25 per cent rise in sales to
Pounds 22.8m. Exports also rose by 25 per cent. Margins were maintained
leading to a 22 per cent rise in operating profits to Pounds 1.65m.
Earnings increased to 2.96p (2.7p) and the interim dividend is a same-again
1.75p.
</TEXT>
