FT  16 JUL 92 / CSO to meet targets
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE Central Statistical Office failed to meet 18 per cent of its performance
targets in 1991-92, according to its annual report published yesterday.
Targets for the CSO, published last November, apply to areas such as size of
